{"tid":1838842,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"細牛醫: 國難忠醫「肥仔」已被釋放","createTime":"2020-01-24T07:17:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-03T18:25:26.000Z","uid":240362,"like":471,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":111,"replies":[{"pid":"9ea0f165cc804833b7f896a249ccbc83ec305000","tid":1838842,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T07:17:20.000Z","msg":"15日已過。<br />\n死肥仔早前打咗電話比我<br />\n話見緊屋企人<br />\n我搵左佢屋企人確認左佢非常安全<br />\n但係<br />\n死肥仔比人困左咁耐感到身心俱疲<br />\n但一條頭髮都無甩到<br />\n簡直係可喜可賀<br />\n暫時個死肥仔唔接受任何訪問<br />\n國難忠醫「暫時」會由我一力承擔<br />\n(吹咩，又係我玩哂)<br />\n佢過多陣就叉完電就會無啦啦突番個死人頭出黎架啦<br />\n<br />\n再次多謝各界人士關心<br />\n感謝各位出手相助既江湖兒女<br />\n<br />\n因admin好攰啦真係<br />\n暫且休養生息<br />\n所以請各位比D空間我地<br />\n細牛本來就好攰<br />\n<br />\n有事請找  @littlecowec"},{"pid":"5cbda204592125cdb8290a4364cf3580d2d58525","tid":1838842,"uid":35456,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T07:18:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1ad266296d7b11a84529684d9d45a55cff4c196b","tid":1838842,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T07:18:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8dbb21fc59210143edfa9bd25fb760b0bab1bd18","tid":1838842,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T07:18:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"21896c7c40743b4c39c9dd8ab59a94179f3da27e","tid":1838842,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T07:18:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"736ec06098c44e66da58a4e804d28f4b456c5c67","tid":1838842,"uid":69741,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T07:18:52.000Z","msg":"會唔會成家比枝槍指住話佢翻咗嚟好安全先"},{"pid":"f53b283438d1e53c601c6a7dd5b7dae3b4f03daa","tid":1838842,"uid":35081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T07:19:12.000Z","msg":"welcome back<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3627e4f26a773f849f103ce6a9d8dae4ecaf5440","tid":1838842,"uid":250508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite